sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant API as API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP
    participant S3 as SeaweedFS/S3<br/>8333/TCP HTTP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow<br/>Controller
    participant Driver as Driver Pod<br/>(Argo Task)
    participant MLMD as metadata-grpc-service<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Launcher as Launcher<br/>(User Container)
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant SWC as Scheduled Workflow<br/>Controller

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,Launcher: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission and Execution
        User->>+API: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>Bearer Token / HTTP Header
        API->>DB: Persist pipeline definition<br/>Username/password auth
        API->>S3: Store compiled pipeline spec<br/>Access key/secret key
        API->>K8s: Create Argo Workflow CR<br/>ServiceAccount token
        API-->>-User: Pipeline run created

        K8s->>Argo: Workflow CR detected
        Argo->>K8s: Create Driver Pod<br/>ServiceAccount token

        activate Driver
        Driver->>MLMD: Resolve inputs, create execution context<br/>gRPC, Optional TLS
        Driver->>API: Cache lookup<br/>gRPC/8887, Optional TLS
        Note right of Driver: On cache miss: generate<br/>pod spec patch for Launcher
        Driver->>K8s: Read Pods, ConfigMaps, Secrets<br/>ServiceAccount token
        deactivate Driver

        activate Launcher
        Launcher->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>HTTP, Secret mount
        Note right of Launcher: Execute user code
        Launcher->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>HTTP, Secret mount
        Launcher->>MLMD: Publish execution results<br/>gRPC, Optional TLS
        Launcher->>API: Register cache entry<br/>gRPC/8887, Optional TLS
        deactivate Launcher
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over PA,API: Flow 2: Persistence Agent Status Reporting
        K8s-->>PA: Watch stream (Argo Workflows,<br/>ScheduledWorkflows)<br/>TLS, ServiceAccount
        PA->>API: Report workflow status<br/>HTTP/8888, Projected SA Token (1h expiry)
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over SWC,API: Flow 3: Scheduled Workflow Execution
        K8s-->>SWC: Watch stream (ScheduledWorkflow CRDs)<br/>TLS, ServiceAccount
        SWC->>K8s: Create Argo Workflow<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount
        SWC->>API: Create run record<br/>gRPC/8887, Projected SA Token
    end
